MAKE MINE A STELLA pressed the early pace three wide, dropped back on the turn and came four wide into the lane, weakened, bested rest. RAIN OF BLESSING chased the early pace, three wide on the turn, came five wide into the lane and weakened. HOME TOWN FAV tracked the early pace two wide, fell back on the turn towards the inside and stopped.
